{"tid":2212456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"增「香港自秦朝已為中國領土」 齡記初中歷史書《基本法》夾硬與古巴比倫苛法掛鈎","createTime":"2020-09-21T23:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T00:27:43.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5feb8bb18e98e361073da2645a67b572c8bd07eb","tid":2212456,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0gCfZby1cR6s2TwURgZrQiqEesw=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SH57WIFSXRASVPEFH5CHQVSRVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0gCfZby1cR6s2TwURgZrQiqEesw%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSH57WIFSXRASVPEFH5CHQVSRVU.jpg&h=7cce29b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n教育局大幅「河蟹」高中通識科教科書有關六四事件、公民抗命等內容後，有今年出版的初中歷史科教科書，將古代歷史與《基本法》掛鈎。在關於約3,700多年前古巴比倫王國制定律法的內容，加插《基本法》指香港居民在法律面前一律平等；又指香港被秦朝劃入版圖，因此《基本法》列明香港特區是中國不可分離的部份。有歷史科老師質疑出版社為了滿足教育局，才加入有關內容。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/USLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FUSLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zER21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=e21e5230\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FUSLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE%2F&h=9bf42bee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/USLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE/</a>"},{"pid":"bca3e886321c6fa57f6bf1952c016f34a3ee7912","tid":2212456,"uid":155095,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:22:17.000Z","msg":"元朝同四大汗國都係中國領土呀，幾時攞返呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://8.blog.xuite.net/8/f/0/3/238211724/blog_3724804/txt/298857277/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail